reviews.text: 服務真差👎
好食，保持水準，但焼味飯太少飯，焼鵝飯個人感覺有點貴！
本以为连锁快餐店出品有点水平，谁知道点个烩牛肉连西兰花都未灼熟。点半只白切鸡鸡肉又太柴，连叉烧都好难食。最后埋单问收银员竟回复说：既不能用银联卡，又不能用支付宝，用人民币的汇率换算竟然是1:1。
好食，不過燒味價錢遍貴，洗手間比較遠要到商場二楼，對行動不便老友記就麻煩啲，不過侍應哥哥超貼心，帶老友記到商埸洗手間，扶出扶入俾個Like你。👍

My friend and I had.a quick late dinner,  we should have gone for their famous barbecue pork etc. Which was what they are known. Instead we went for their Hong Kong tea house style menu,  the spam macaroni was so tasteless,  and the spare ride noodles was a.gooey mess. Service was patchy too,  give that a miss!

reviews.text: Washroom can be found each floor except ground floor. But too many hawkers at entrance. If crowded people .There was no space to walk through. Food place is good to choice. Chinese , dim sum, simple food store. Fried pork chop , or tea .
Very modern shopping plaza with some nice restaurants
generally ok but somehow crowdy n many GC tourists
A local mall in Mong kok, very crowded all the time, not easy to get a table during dinner time. There aren't something very spectacular that attracts customers

Sushi quality is good in general.  most of the sushi feature with a longer piece of sashimi. Fish quality is geat  The Red Roll is my favorite.  The miso soap is nice too with good quality of seaweed and quite different from what I use to have in different stores.  The reason for a 3- star is that it is a bit overpriced though.  Almost HK$300 per head is a bit too much.
